query:
SELECT hostname, landing_page, SUM(sessions) as total_sessions, date
FROM ga4_landing_page_metrics 
WHERE hostname LIKE '%31daywisdomchallenge%'
GROUP BY hostname, landing_page, date
ORDER BY total_sessions DESC
LIMIT 10
